        "description": "Similar to ARROW-15106 but observed from the client, not the server.\r\n\r\nThe Python Flight client blocks the thread and ignores signal handlers. This makes it impossible for the client to handle the signal handler and cancel the query before it has returned a FlightStreamReader.",
